metadata.name: KAPC #1
metadata.description: KAPC is a collection of 10,000 children apes on the Ethereum Blockchain. All apes will start out as Baby apes, but you will get the chance to age them all the way up to a teen. The age groups will consist of Baby apes, Toddler apes, Kid apes, and Teen apes. Each age group will have it's unique traits as well as universal traits that can be generated at any age. We value transparency, fairness, and support within the community. Thank you for your support
